ius Bjornsson]]\n[[Category:Brei\u00f0ablik men's basketball players|Hafthor Julius Bjornsson]]\n[[Category:KR men's basketball players|Hafthor Julius Bjornsson]]\n", "name_user": "204.14.101.168", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eFamily and relationships)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haf%C3%BE%C3%B3r_J%C3%BAl%C3%ADus_Bj%C3%B6rnsson"}
